  <brief_title>The Effect of Sildenafil in Preterm Infants With Evolving Chronic Lung Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Sildenafil in Preterm Infants With Evolving Chronic Lung Disease (SPICE Trial): a Pilot Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
