  <source>Mercy Hospital for Women, Australia</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this pilot study is to investigate in a randomised double-blind trial whether
      treatment with Sildenafil reduces duration of ventilatory support in preterm infants born at
      28 weeks of gestation or less.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
