  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Newborn babies born &lt;28 weeks of gestation who still need ventilatory support via
             endotracheal tube or have been re-ventilated at day 7 of life.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Congenital heart defects

          -  Suspected inborn error of metabolism

          -  Inhaled Nitric Oxide treatment during assessment
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
